text: Nakontrol na saray player iray aksyon tan kiwas ed video games no igalaw dad dagem so device.
translated_text:
Pangasinan: Nakontrol na saray player iray aksyon tan kiwas ed video games no igalaw dad dagem so device. 
English: In Singapore, the government has banned the sale of video games to children under the age of 13.

text: Manga 100 ya totoo so inmatendi ed party, pian selebraan so unonan anibersaryo na sanasawa ya nankasal nen imbeneg ya taon.
translated_text:
Pangasinan: Manga 100 ya totoo so inmatendi ed party, pian selebraan so unonan anibersaryo na sanasawa ya nankasal nen imbeneg ya taon. 
English: The 100th anniversary of the founding of the Republic of Singapore was marked by a series of events, including a parade, a musical and a party.

text: Saray duaran kansion ya inusar ed pelikula, say Audition (The Fools Who Dream) tan City of Stars, at a-nominate parad best original song. Say Lionsgate studio et 26 ya beses ya a-nominate — mas dakel nen say anggan anton studio.
translated_text:
Pangasinan: Saray duaran kansion ya inusar ed pelikula, say Audition (The Fools Who Dream) tan City of Stars, at a-nominate parad best original song. Say Lionsgate studio et 26 ya beses ya a-nominate — mas dakel nen say anggan anton studio. 
English: Saray duaran kansion ya inusar ed pelikula, say Audition (The Fools Who Dream) tan City of Stars, at a-nominate parad best original song. Say Lionsgate studio et 26 ya beses ya a-nominate — mas dakel nen say anggan anton studio.

text: Say inkaupiyas to et mga 70km kapal ed tapew tan 100km kapal diad gilig.

text: Say South Pole Traverse (odino Highway) so walaan na 1600km trail manlapud McMurdo Station on the Ross sea anggad Pole.
translated_text:

English: Traverse: Traverse is a trail that runs along the South Pole. It is 1600km long and is a popular trail for the South Pole Traverse Trail.

text: Matatayug diad bandad amianen na parten amianen na Machu Picchu so ayan atagey a palandey ya maslak ya sa backdrop na litrato na saray ageba.

English: The Machu Picchu is a UNESCO World Heritage Site and is a UNESCO World Heritage Site of the Humanity.

text: Say Enceladus so sankanengneng ed solar system, manre-reflect so manga 90 porsyento na sinag na agew ya ontamad sikato.
translated_text:

text: Nen mansampot la, say Bagyon Gonu et nginaranan ya bag na bulong ya palma diad lenguahe na Maldives ta nabot tan apansiansia toy dagem ya 240 kilometros kada oras (149 ya milya kada oras).
translated_text:

English: The island is a popular holiday destination for the wealthy and the elite, and is home to the world's largest hotel, the Four Seasons Maldives.

text: Say sukat na Turkey, kaiba la ray lawa, et 783,562 square kilometres (300,948 sq mi), ya say 755,688 square kilometres (291,773 sq mi) et walad south west Asia tan say 23,764 square kilometres (9,174 sq mi) et diad Europe.
translated_text:
Pangasinan: Say sukat na Turkey, kaiba la ray lawa, et 783,562 square kilometres (300,948 sq mi), ya say 755,688 square kilometres (291,773 sq mi) et walad south west Asia tan say 23,764 square kilometres (9,174 sq mi) et diad Europe. 
English: Turkey is a country in the Middle East, located in the western part of the Mediterranean Sea.

text: Saray Isla ed South Shetland ya adiskobre nen 1819 et sinakop na pigaran bansa tan walaan na sankarakelan ya base na militar, ya labin-anem so aktibo nen 2020.

English: South Shetland: Saray Isla is a small island in the South Shetland archipelago in the Indian Ocean.

text: Say Apia so capital na Samoa. Say baley na satan et walad isla na Upolu tan walaan labat na populasyon ya ag-onabet ed 40,000.
